s derive the first part from the Germanic word <i>gawia</i> ‘territory’, <i>walah</i> ‘stranger’, or <i>gisil</i> ‘pledge’. Medieval forms can be found to support all these theories, and it is possible that several names have fallen together, or that the name was subjected to reanalysis by folk etymology at an early date."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Geoffrey Loveday married Geoffrey Loveday before 1326, in England. They were the parents of at least 1 son."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1308–1326":"1308–1326","1326–1352":"1326–1352","–Female":"Surnud","before 1326":"enne 1326","1326":"1326","1352":"1352","1308":"1308","Shrivenham, Berkshire, England":"Shrivenham, Berkshire, England","England":"England"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1308–1326":"1308–1326","1326–1352":"1326–1352","–Female":"Kuollut","before 1326":"ennen vuotta 1326","1326":"1326","1352":"1352","1308":"1308","Shrivenham, Berkshire, England":"Shrivenham, Berkshire, England","England":"England"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1308–1326":"1308–1326","1326–1352":"1326–1352","–Female":"Décédée","before 1326":"avant 1326","1326":"1326","1352":"1352","1308":"1308","Shrivenham, Berkshire, England":"Shrivenham, Berkshire, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Mrs Geoffrey Loveday a épousé Geoffrey Loveday avant 1326, à Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fils."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1308–1326":"1308–1326","1326–1352":"1326–1352","–Female":"Verstorben","before 1326":"vor 1326","1326":"1326","1352":"1352","1308":"1308","Shrivenham, Berkshire, England":"Shrivenham, Berkshire, England","England":"England","lifeSummary":"Mrs Geoffrey Loveday hat vor 1326 in England Geoffrey Loveday geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","1308–1326":"1308–1326","1326–1352":"1326–1352","–Female":"Desede","before 1326":"before 1326","1326":"1326","1352":"1352","1308":"1308","Shrivenham, Berkshire, England":"Shrivenham, Berkshire, England","England":"England"},"hu":{"–":"elhunyt","1308–1326":"1308–1326","1326–1352":"13